    "type": "paragraph",
    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "I realize that I couldn’t have done a better job of finding a early morning sunny spot to put my tent. Last night’s beers and a thirty degree 6am isn’t winning combination. I relocate outside and the rest comes easily. Two doves position themselves dangerously close to directly above me. ",
            "link": null
          },
